==English==
===Proper noun===
'''[[Azerbaijan]] [[Soviet Socialist Republic|SSR]]'''
# Azerbaijan Soviet Socialist Republic, the name for [[Azerbaijan]] while under the rule of the [[Soviet Union]] (1936-1991, name changed in 1990).

